{"tid":824824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布明日所有學校繼續停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T03:56:22.000Z","uid":49974,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4765a5be6e820a42fb918e27f0b34770c4fd6b5c","tid":824824,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1030830&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1030830%26csid%3D261_341&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=cfc90b5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1030830&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n教育局宣布，明日所有學校繼續停課。局方指，由於強颱風山竹對學校造成不同程度影響，部分學校需時清理及維修校舍和設施，加上公共交通服務尚待完全恢復正常，為確保學生的安全，明日所有學校停課。<br />\n<br />\n在安全的情況下，學校應保持校舍開放，並實施校本應急計劃，安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生。家長應考慮家居環境、附近的道路交通情況、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女回校。"},{"pid":"236c277dfc9c9c949ef9c52f6b9dc81c922b728c","tid":824824,"uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f43091b2fe7880686689cc9599f28f19ba4db4","tid":824824,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b4af920b341b76eb959f738418b605232e79e2","tid":824824,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2930508bc8857da8bdf3ac54b2f5cbee7b45ea","tid":824824,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal